text: Lyuben Khristov (born 15 July 1935) is a Bulgarian gymnast. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sofia
